{
  "stem": "14251.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So it was always dismal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you waited until finally your mother or father came to get you, everything in a rush because there were only certain hours you were allowed out on the street.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in some cases, the child was left standing simply because the parents had been picked up at their forced labor place.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And now, you know, this child couldn't make the connection until probably the next day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some overseeing person luckily always stayed around long enough till we were all picked up or-- or accounted for in some way with an adult person.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you knew what was going on, but you didn't understand what was going on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the way your parents hugged you and kissed you to say hello when they picked you up-- and they took turns at that.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One had to go get the food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Remember, there were no refrigerators.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So every day, you had to hassle on that limited diet that you had, in limited stores in which you could obtain them, which were all sold out or they didn't have it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, the other parent worried about, is the-- my child still at the kindergarten when I get there?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you could feel that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could feel that by the way they clung to you in a desperate kind of a sensation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, you can tell that, but you don't understand why.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did you have any friends that you can recall that disappeared?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, actually.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's a little boy I remember named Michael.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or in German, it was Mikhail.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was always sort of looking out for me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was, I think, a year older than I was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother cannot remember the family's last name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have asked her.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
